Time.Piece.Cron
===============

Perl Time::Piece::Cron module

Parse and evaluate times from crontab-like time specifier strings.



Synopsis
===============

use Time::Piece;
use Time::Piece::Cron;

my $cron = Time::Piece::Cron->new();
my $bool = $cron->is_now("08 30 * * *");
my $timepiece = $cron->next_time("00 00 * 07 Mon");



Install
===============

perl Build.PL
./Build
./Build test
./Build install


